Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.01,0:24:56.02,screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs110\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,700)}来自过去的礼物
